To complement the tantalizing photographs of each essential cocktail, DeGroff also regales readers with the fascinating lore behind a drinkÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s genesis and instructs us on using the right ingredients, techniques, glasses, and garnishes. As Julia ChildÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Mastering the Art of French Cooking was the classic compendium for home chefs and gourmands, so The Essential Cocktail will be the go-to book for serious mixologists and cocktail enthusiasts.
